pull_request.title: Landing plus
pull_request.body:
This pull request introduces several enhancements and refactors across the codebase, focusing on privacy/structured data, improved consent banner accessibility and progressive enhancement, custom scrollbar utilities, and the addition of a new projects showcase section. The changes improve semantic data, user experience, accessibility, and code maintainability.

**Privacy & Structured Data Improvements**
* Added `assets/privacy-structured-data.json` and `assets/structured-data.json` to provide Schema.org structured data for privacy policy and personal profile, improving SEO and semantic clarity. [[1]](diffhunk://#diff-37e95d53b9488d0fec4c0f0708bc6a206601e165059d84299714cd822a526191R1-R10) [[2]](diffhunk://#diff-5137a273973618b9b8ed7bd64a3389fac73e26243808d9ddaceb56882944c182R1-R8)

**Consent Banner & Dialog Accessibility and Progressive Enhancement**
* Refactored `css/components/consent-banner.css` to use progressive enhancement for backgrounds and blur effects, improved focus styles, added keyboard accessibility, and enhanced support for reduced motion and high contrast users. Also added `.no-js` and `.js` classes for toggling settings visibility, and improved print handling. [[1]](diffhunk://#diff-acd05e3e38f08d9d99a9e47e1753a824658a57a56ca14ba0e3aee39fbf968ce9L51-R69) [[2]](diffhunk://#diff-acd05e3e38f08d9d99a9e47e1753a824658a57a56ca14ba0e3aee39fbf968ce9L134-R171) [[3]](diffhunk://#diff-acd05e3e38f08d9d99a9e47e1753a824658a57a56ca14ba0e3aee39fbf968ce9R274-R284) [[4]](diffhunk://#diff-acd05e3e38f08d9d99a9e47e1753a824658a57a56ca14ba0e3aee39fbf968ce9R311-R316) [[5]](diffhunk://#diff-acd05e3e38f08d9d99a9e47e1753a824658a57a56ca14ba0e3aee39fbf968ce9L326-R381) [[6]](diffhunk://#diff-acd05e3e38f08d9d99a9e47e1753a824658a57a56ca14ba0e3aee39fbf968ce9R416-R427) [[7]](diffhunk://#diff-acd05e3e38f08d9d99a9e47e1753a824658a57a56ca14ba0e3aee39fbf968ce9R477-R495) [[8]](diffhunk://#diff-acd05e3e38f08d9d99a9e47e1753a824658a57a56ca14ba0e3aee39fbf968ce9L476-R543) [[9]](diffhunk://#diff-acd05e3e38f08d9d99a9e47e1753a824658a57a56ca14ba0e3aee39fbf968ce9R615-L629) [[10]](diffhunk://#diff-acd05e3e38f08d9d99a9e47e1753a824658a57a56ca14ba0e3aee39fbf968ce9R687-R694) [[11]](diffhunk://#diff-acd05e3e38f08d9d99a9e47e1753a824658a57a56ca14ba0e3aee39fbf968ce9R710-R795)

* Added a new analytics switch control with custom styles for toggling consent, including accessibility and responsive design improvements.

**Custom Scrollbar Utilities**
* Updated `css/components/custom-scrollbar.css` to add `.hide-scrollbar` utility for element-specific scrollbar hiding, and a global opt-in class for site-wide hidden scrollbars, improving flexibility and cross-browser support. [[1]](diffhunk://#diff-df94d51c46a47e3d4b7a75545ac83f1e5ec88ea5a912b6f6d5f25f9a5482b8e3R53-R72) [[2]](diffhunk://#diff-df94d51c46a47e3d4b7a75545ac83f1e5ec88ea5a912b6f6d5f25f9a5482b8e3L109-R137)

**Projects Showcase Section**
* Added a new projects section to `css/components/hero.css`, including responsive grid, card styles, and focus/hover effects for improved presentation and accessibility.

**Minor Variable Addition**
* Added a serif font variable `--font-serif` in `css/base/variables.css` for improved typography options.

**Other**
* Removed the `.vscode/tasks.json` file, cleaning up unused editor configuration.

pull_request.title: Refactor: Simplify profile feature navigation
pull_request.body:
This commit refactors the navigation within the profile feature by:

- Removing the dedicated `ProfileNavGraph` and its associated navigator classes (`ProfileNavigator`, `ProfileNavigatorImpl`, `ProfileNavigationEvent`, etc.).
- Introducing a `ProfileDestinationActivity` to handle navigation to `WatchHistoryScreen` and `MyRatingScreen`.
- Navigation to these screens is now done by launching `ProfileDestinationActivity` with the target `Destination` serialized as a JSON string in the Intent extras.
- The `ProfileScreen` is now the direct entry point for the profile feature.
- `BaseViewModel` no longer holds a reference to `ProfileNavigator`.
- Updated `WatchHistoryScreen` and `MyRatingScreen` to use `LocalActivity.current.finish()` for back navigation instead of the ViewModel.
- Added serialization dependency for Kotlinx Serialization.
- Updated `ProfileViewModel` and `ProfileScreen` to use the new navigation mechanism.
- Removed `onBackClick` from `MyRatingViewModel`, `WatchHistoryViewModel`, and their respective interaction listeners.
- Moved `InstallSavedAppLanguage.kt` and `MainViewModel.kt` to a more general `main` package.
- Removed unused `BaseViewModel.kt` from `utils` package and `ObserveAsEvents.kt`.
